{"tid":1258074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我認為需要大肆宣傳對家嘅「文革」式舉動","createTime":"2019-06-26T02:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T02:59:53.000Z","uid":49781,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"32f47010b01e85e2b66a4198fedc2844d173c68f","tid":1258074,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:10:14.000Z","msg":"我相信香港老一輩有唔少人都係經歷過中共文革而逃難到香港，<br />\n所以文革呢樣嘢對佢哋來講係痛苦、災難式歷史，<br />\n對家嘅文革手段好明顯：造假新聞、製假影片、網軍打手等，企圖帶動不利我哋嘅輿論同製造世代對立，<br />\n我哋必須刻意提點所有人浮現緊嘅文革式行為，例如可以整「古今文革對比圖」、長輩圖長輩片、同自己家人講等等，甚至同外國朋友講，<br />\n總之就係要將「文革」呢個詞語同呢班垃圾嘅行為扣上（因為係事實來），以減低佢哋嘅殺傷力。"},{"pid":"9f8f3744cff36509424781b8600f739a59b4f411","tid":1258074,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:10:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3f3ec5078779313071a78e739544c97b7d71709","tid":1258074,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:32:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a9616dd8e25a0e68a38ca30a2b3aff3ce230137","tid":1258074,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:34:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96d34067ee85e60ab752b285c5a059bbb07a63ec","tid":1258074,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"push ar"},{"pid":"bc1aa8854071d584a601d5e25b0eeb976a3fd7ee","tid":1258074,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:42:48.000Z","msg":"文宣組！！！"},{"pid":"e54a611f32505fca65fafaca34dfd6902af0cf6b","tid":1258074,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:59:53.000Z","msg":"大家有咩意見"}]}